Welcome to Mega Bites, where flavors take flight, A cozy kitchen, serving meals day and night. From bites so big to treats so sweet, Each dish we serve is a savory feat.
With love and care, our food's prepared, In every bite, you’ll find we’ve shared, A passion for cooking, bold and bright, Bringing joy with every bite.
Come on by, don't hesitate, Mega Bites will make your day great! Quick, delicious, with flavors divine, A little bite of happiness every time!
